		<div>The resist rate on Wildmagic has been fixed, Airanemyer.  It is a very good spell now.  Wildmagic is a 3 second cast spell and is SO much more efficient than Sothgar's (7.67 unfocused, compared to 4.97) that it is really not too surprising that it is an all-around better spell.<br />
<br />
And yes, in a group you can usually catch a tick or two of OOC regen between pulls, and then med to full when the cleric also needs mana.  So you may afford to use the very high mana per second patterns--that is the ones with lots of instants mixed in with a few other spells.</div>
