*nod*, and the surprising conclusion I came to is that a mix of FF, Wildmagic and CBS will outperform any of those mixtures.  In all cases short of chain-instant-as-fast-as-you-can-and-still-can't-go-oom, EC on GORM procs produces a better result than an instant, if only marginally (a difference of a few percent damage).<br />
<br />
The change from (Soth+FF) to (FF+(Wild|CBS)) is a significant power boost, however.  A wizard going all-out (Soth+FF) could, in the same amount of time and with the same amount of mana, do a good ~150 more DPS.</div>
