IE procs Intertwining Power with 25% chance and Intertwining Weakness with 1% chance. Power overrides your BUFF dmg focus with 100% (i.e. if you had a flappy or a bard - you get 100% instead of 30% for the next nuke), and you still have your WORN focus intact. Weakness overrides BUFF focus with -50% (i.e. you go from 30% to -50% on that value). Power affects your 1 next nuke. Weakness affects all nukes for 2 ticks.</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
